Hungry Horse are part of The Great British Pub Card. At Hungry Horse, we’re all about sitting back, relaxing and sharing great times with friends and family. You will feel right at home with us – but you don’t have to worry about cooking for yourself or doing the washing up either! The Great British Pub Card is the leading pub gift card that can be redeemed against food, drink or accommodation in over 3000 locations nationwide. Including brands such as Chef & Brewer, Loch Fyne, Flaming Grill, Hungry Horse and many others. The Great British Pub Card is also available to purchase as a digital code, its flexible and offers a vast choice of food, drink or dining opportunities. Perfect for celebrating those special times with family, catching-up with friends or meeting with colleagues. For more information visit www.greatbritishpubcard.co.uk.